Apache-2.0 notice summary
=========================

Bundled Alpine packages currently identified with Apache-2.0 metadata:

  - openssl
  - libcrypto3
  - libssl3

At the time this compliance bundle was prepared, no standalone NOTICE file
was detected inside the redistributed Alpine binary APK archives for those
packages. This file is therefore provided as a tracking note for the Apache
License redistribution requirement.

When package versions change, re-check the corresponding source packages and
package metadata pages listed in SOURCE_LOCATIONS to confirm whether upstream
NOTICE content must also be reproduced.
